;
; Access Control Configuration
;
; Currently supported directives:
;
; ban <ip>              - Block a specific IP address
; ban <network>/<bits>  - Block a network range using CIDR notation
;
; Examples:
;
; Block a single nuisance user
; ban 192.168.0.55
;
; Block an entire subnet
; ban 10.0.0.0/8
;
; Block a specific range
; ban 172.16.0.0/12
;
